{"word":"G2452 - Ἰουδαϊκῶς - Ioudaïkōs - ee-oo-dah-ee-koce' - As do the Jews","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">Ἰουδαϊκῶς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">Ioudaïkōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ee-oo-dah-ee-koce'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">As do the Jews</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"யூதர் முறைமையாக - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"Jewishly, after the manner of the Jews"},{"paragraph":"\"யூதருடைய\""},{"paragraph":"\"Jewish\""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G2451 - Ἰουδαϊκός - Ioudaïkós - ee-oo-dah-ee-kos'/2451\">G2451</a>; <i>Judaically</i> or <i>in a manner resembling a Judaean:</i> - as do the Jews.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2448/2448\">G2448</a>, <a href=\"#/G2449/2449\">G2449</a>, <a href=\"#/G2450/2450\">G2450</a>, <a href=\"#/G2451/2451\">G2451</a>, <a href=\"#/G2452/2452\">G2452</a>, <a href=\"#/G2453/2453\">G2453</a>, <a href=\"#/G2454/2454\">G2454</a>"}]}